data.description: Stunning 5-Bedroom Home in The Preserve of Harbins Ridge  Welcome to 3527 Parkside View Blvd, Dacula, GA 30019, a remarkable 5-bedroom, 4-bathroom, 3,080 sq ft home nestled on a generous .34-acre lot in The Preserve of Harbins Ridge, one of the most coveted communities in the highly sought-after Archer High School district. This Benjamin plan residence boasts numerous modern amenities, and it's priced to sell! Don't miss your chance to make this your dream home.  Key Features:  Spacious Living: This home offers an abundance of space for your family with 5 bedrooms, 4 bathrooms, and large common areas. With hardwood floors throughout the main level, you'll enjoy a seamless flow from room to room.  Gourmet Kitchen: The heart of this home is the beautifully appointed kitchen featuring granite countertops, a tile backsplash, an island with ample counter space, and stainless steel appliances. Double ovens make entertaining a breeze.  Cozy Family Room: The open-concept layout allows the kitchen to flow effortlessly into the family room, where you'll find a cozy fireplace, perfect for gatherings and relaxation.  Main Floor Master: The spacious master suite on the main level is a true retreat, offering privacy and comfort. A half bath on the main floor adds to the convenience of the layout.  Generous Bedrooms: Upstairs, you'll find large secondary bedrooms, each with ample closet space and natural light. There's room for everyone to have their space.  Exterior Appeal: The home features an elegant brick front and a sprinkler system to keep your lawn lush and green. It also includes a Smart Home package for added convenience.  As-Is Sale: The property is being sold as-is, offering a fantastic opportunity for you to personalize and make it your own.  Ideal Location:  This home is ideally located in The Preserve of Harbins Ridge, a community known for its family-friendly atmosphere and top-rated schools. Enjoy the convenience of being in the Archer High School district, ensuring a quality education for your family.  Priced to Sell:  This fantastic property is priced to sell, with cash offers preferred and a quick closing desired. Don't miss the opportunity to own this spacious, modern home in a prime location.  For more information or to schedule a showing, please contact us today. This home won't stay on the market for long, so act quickly and make it yours!
